5
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,860
You still can't forget her?

6
00:01:44,860 --> 00:01:46,040
She's long forgotten.

7
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:48,079
I didn't even say who.

8
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:50,040
Why are you so eager to admit it?

9
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:53,059
Is it that female doctor?

10
00:01:53,059 --> 00:01:54,559
No.

11
00:01:55,272 --> 00:01:57,719
I don't believe you.

12
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:59,549
I saw you two chatting.

13
00:01:59,549 --> 00:02:01,249
I don't know her.

14
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:03,979
You say one thing but mean another.

15
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:07,580
What are you laughing about?

16
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:08,795
I'm happy.

17
00:02:08,795 --> 00:02:10,964
It's good that you're no longer single.

18
00:02:10,964 --> 00:02:14,240
Now that you're taken, I can set my wedding date.

19
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,400
What are you thinking?

20
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,840
You go ahead and get married.

21
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,540
Why wait for me?

22
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:23,980
How come that sounded a bit heartbreaking?

23
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,580
An ex-girlfriend?

24
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,943
I guess that means yes.

25
00:02:40,943 --> 00:02:44,446
She looks quite pretty and has a good presence.

26
00:02:44,446 --> 00:02:46,746
So why did you two break up?

27
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:50,079
Time for night shift patrol.

28
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:54,140
Wait up. I'll go with you!

29
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:22,219
 Try it. 

30
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,619
 It's sour. 

31
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:29,609
 Yet sweet. 

32
00:03:29,609 --> 00:03:30,944
 This taste... 

33
00:03:30,944 --> 00:03:32,979
 It's amazing. 

34
00:03:41,688 --> 00:03:43,699
 Try one. 

35
00:03:43,699 --> 00:03:46,625
 If you don't like it, I'll pay with my life. 

36
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,739
 Amazing. 

37
00:04:08,739 --> 00:04:10,339
 Isn't it? 

38
