00:26:50,600 --> 00:26:51,880
 You must be dumb. 

327
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,759
 Look. 

328
00:26:52,759 --> 00:26:54,140
 It's not "o," but "u." 

329
00:26:54,140 --> 00:26:56,860
 You wrote "son" instead of "sun." 

330
00:27:02,079 --> 00:27:04,599
 So how are you going to explain this? 

331
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:10,799
 If you smile, the son fills the city. 

