00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,840
 Who is it? 

341
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:18,340
 Who is it? 

342
00:28:21,759 --> 00:28:23,620
What are you doing here?

343
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:26,907
Zhai Miao?

344
00:28:26,907 --> 00:28:28,910
You've grown up so much.

345
00:28:30,359 --> 00:28:31,743
Why are you here?

346
00:28:31,743 --> 00:28:33,680
I’m here to find Song Yan.

347
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:35,440
Song Yan? What for?

348
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,880
You still have the audacity to come here?

349
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:39,319
Have you forgotten what you did?

350
00:28:39,319 --> 00:28:40,920
Whatever. I don't want to talk to you.

351
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:43,449
- He's not here. 
 - Wait! Zhao Miao.

352
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:53,160
When will he be back?

353
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,720
That's none of your business.

354
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:58,279
Miss Xu, my cousin is living a good life right now. He might be getting married next year.

355
00:28:58,279 --> 00:28:59,699
So leave him alone, will you?

356
00:28:59,699 --> 00:29:00,880
I'll thank you for that.

357
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,580
Zhai Miao!

358
00:29:07,839 --> 00:29:09,239
Auntie.

359
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,660
Song Yan doesn't live here anymore.

360
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:14,680
Then where does he live?

361
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,455
Could you tell me?

362
00:29:16,455 --> 00:29:18,400
He's usually at the station.

363
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:20,319
He doesn't come back often.

364
00:29:58,997 --> 00:30:01,400
Mom, what's the matter?

365
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,599
She looked like a tortured soul.

366
00:30:03,599 --> 00:30:06,839
Do you think I was too harsh on her?

367
00:30:06,839 --> 00:30:08,440
You call that being harsh?

368
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:11,580
If it were me, I'd say worse things to her.

369
00:30:11,580 --> 00:30:13,079
Why would I do that?

370
00:30:13,079 --> 00:30:15,839
Why? Did you forget what she did to my cousin?

371
00:30:15,839 --> 00:30:17,980
I've never met anyone more evil than her.

372
00:30:17,980 --> 00:30:20,179
How dare she come here.

373
00:30:20,179 --> 00:30:24,079
Didn't she go overseas to study? How come she's back all of a sudden?

374
00:30:24,079 --> 00:30:26,919
I wonder why she needs to see your cousin.

375
00:30:28,279 --> 00:30:29,440
Maybe she feels guilty.

376
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:33,039
With that cold and aloof attitude of hers, it'd be hard not to dislike her.

377
00:30:33,039 --> 00:30:35,559
Only my dumb cousin would consider her a gem.

378
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:37,969
Now that she has realized no one likes her,

379
00:30:37,969 --> 00:30:39,799
she remembers how well my cousin treated her.

380
00:30:39,799 --> 00:30:43,319
I was wondering why your cousin has been acting so strange lately.

381
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:47,079
Do you think he still likes her?

382
00:30:47,079 --> 00:30:48,240
No way.

383
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:51,680
My cousin must hate her to the core. How could he still like her?

384
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:53,000
You have no idea.

385
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:55,519
These past years, I've tried to set him up on many blind dates.

386
00:30:55,519 --> 00:31:00,480
He either said he was too busy to go, or he wasn't interested after meeting them.

387
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:02,039
There's no way.

388
00:31:02,039 --> 00:31:04,396
Even if my cousin will be single all his life, he cannot be nice to her.

389
00:31:04,396 --> 00:31:06,133
Did he forget how much he suffered because of her?

390
00:31:06,133 --> 00:31:07,133
This is...

391
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:10,804
This won't do. I'm going to talk some sense into him.

392
00:31:10,804 --> 00:31:13,319
- He likes being tortured, huh? I won't have... 
 - Wait!

393
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:17,779
Young lady. Stay out of your cousin's business.

394
00:31:24,119 --> 00:31:26,800
Stop shaking your leg. Go study!

395
00:32:00,230 --> 00:32:02,954
Doctor, my baby got burned. Please treat her quickly.

396
00:32:02,954 --> 00:32:04,314
Did you get a number?

397
00:32:04,314 --> 00:32:05,600
You need a number for emergency care?

398
00:32:05,600 --> 00:32:06,920
Yes, you need to register for emergency care too.

399
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:09,240
What a stupid hospital. I got burned to this extent!

400
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,519
Sir, please register her.

401
00:32:10,519 --> 00:32:12,079
Or else the system cannot issue her prescription.

402
00:32:12,079 --> 00:32:14,720
Fine. Wait for me.

403
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:16,440
Please wait outside. Thanks.

404
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,340
Please wait outside.

405
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:25,879
- Get the medicine first and then get her an injection. 
 - Okay.

406
00:32:25,879 --> 00:32:28,680
Next time you get bitten by a dog, you can go directly to the CDC.

407
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:30,000
No need to come to the general hospital.

408
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:32,300
Okay, thanks.

409
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:38,559
Doctor, quick!

410
00:32:38,559 --> 00:32:40,119
Please take a look.

411
00:32:40,119 --> 00:32:41,978
I've got a big red patch from the burn.

412
00:32:41,978 --> 00:32:42,928
How did it happen?

413
00:32:42,928 --> 00:32:45,000
I accidentally got burned by the hot water.

414
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:46,800
Did it just happen?

415
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:50,119
I registered. Here.

416
00:32:50,119 --> 00:32:52,540
It's all right. Let me give it a blow.

417
00:32:55,559 --> 00:32:57,759
Will it leave a scar?

418
00:32:57,759 --> 00:33:00,044
Don't worry. Relax.

419
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,440
Here, this is the prescription.

420
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,680
Go take the medicine as prescribed.

421
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:06,160
That's it? That's all?

422
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:07,961
Your wound is not serious. You'll be fine after using the topical cream for three days.

423
00:33:07,961 --> 00:33:09,960
But it's a huge red patch!

424
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:10,881
- Dr. Xu. 
 - Yes?

425
00:33:10,881 --> 00:33:12,995
This firefighter is injured quite badly. Please take a look.

426
00:33:12,995 --> 00:33:14,519
Check him.

427
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:16,980
Doctor.

428
00:33:19,069 --> 00:33:21,640
Go to the debridement room and get ready for sutures.

429
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:23,599
Doctor! What about my wife?

430
00:33:23,599 --> 00:33:26,720
I gave you the prescription, didn't I? Just get the medicine stated there.

431
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,519
You barely checked for a minute.

432
00:33:28,519 --> 00:33:31,660
Your injury is nothing serious. Use the prescribed medicine and it'll be fine.

433
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,359
Did you really treat my wife's condition?

434
00:33:34,359 --> 00:33:35,659
It was barely 10 seconds.

435
00:33:35,659 --> 00:33:37,300
I don't have time to argue with you right now.

436
00:33:37,300 --> 00:33:38,466
Let's go.

437
00:33:38,466 --> 00:33:41,631
Stop right there! So you're not treating my wife, are you?

438
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:47,279
Are you being rough on a woman? Didn't your parents teach you better?

439
00:33:47,279 --> 00:33:49,720
Who are you? I'm looking for her.

440
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:50,799
Are you done?

441
00:33:50,799 --> 00:33:53,419
Let go of my husband!

442
00:33:55,119 --> 00:33:57,960
Remember your job. Don't just stand here and ogle.

443
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,659
Go and get your medicine.

444
00:33:59,659 --> 00:34:01,379
Let's hurry.

445
00:34:01,379 --> 00:34:02,879
I'll wait here.

446
00:34:08,346 --> 00:34:10,960
Hang in there. I'll inject the anesthetic soon.

447
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:12,100
Thanks, Doctor.

448
00:34:12,100 --> 00:34:14,039
Let me clean you up.

449
00:34:14,039 --> 00:34:16,399
Come. Lift your arm.

450
00:34:20,699 --> 00:34:22,400
Don't move around.

451
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:24,120
This hand is fine. I can do it myself.

452
00:34:24,120 --> 00:34:25,559
No, this hand is still swollen.

453
00:34:25,559 --> 00:34:28,519
It's dirty. I can't let you do it yourself.

454
00:34:31,039 --> 00:34:34,039
What happened to your arm?

455
00:34:34,039 --> 00:34:35,179
Someone tried to jump off a bridge.

456
00:34:35,179 --> 00:34:37,440
Thank goodness nothing bad happened. We saved him.

457
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:39,199
Wasn't there any ambulance on the scene?

458
00:34:39,199 --> 00:34:42,719
I didn't see one. My colleague just bundled me up and brought me here.

459
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:44,960
You should make a complaint if no ambulance went there.

460
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:48,559
Wait a minute, Dr. Xu. The ambulance and us are under the same roof.

461
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:49,779
Right.

462
00:34:49,779 --> 00:34:52,559
When calamity strikes, we're all in the same boat.

463
00:34:52,559 --> 00:34:54,320
There's no reason to point fingers.

464
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:58,919
You doctors and us firefighters, we're all family, right?

465
00:34:58,919 --> 00:35:00,360
It's tough for all of us.

466
00:35:00,360 --> 00:35:02,940
I'm injecting the anesthetic.

467
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:06,160
Please be gentle. I don't like needles.

468
00:35:19,519 --> 00:35:21,819
Where were you just now?

469
00:35:22,887 --> 00:35:26,627
That man was being unreasonable and was about to hit the doctor. Didn't you see?

470
00:35:26,627 --> 00:35:28,100
It wasn't like that. I was...

471
00:35:28,100 --> 00:35:30,580
If I hadn't come, would you have let her get beaten up?

472
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:31,900
No way, Boss.

473
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:33,000
Anyway, nothing happened.

474
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:34,480
I'm not your boss.

475
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,100
You're my boss.

476
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:37,700
Hey...

477
00:35:39,679 --> 00:35:41,520
Hang on.

478
00:35:43,500 --> 00:35:45,600
Do you know that doctor?

479
00:35:48,079 --> 00:35:49,440
No, I don't.

480
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:52,200
If you don't, why are you so worried about her?

481
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:12,920
- How is it, Old Jiang? 
 - I'm all right.

482
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,239
Thanks, Doctor.

483
00:36:14,239 --> 00:36:15,760
Pay the fees and then get the anti-inflammatory medication.

484
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:19,160
Got it. Thanks, Nurse and Doctor.

485
00:36:19,160 --> 00:36:20,370
Are you looking for someone?

486
00:36:20,370 --> 00:36:22,770
Our captain just left. He went that way.

487
00:36:24,599 --> 00:36:26,420
Go get your medication.

488
00:36:26,420 --> 00:36:27,254
Thank you.

489
00:36:27,254 --> 00:36:29,440
We'll be off then. Thanks, Nurse.

490
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:31,240
Are you okay?

491
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:37,739
I'm taking over, Dr. Xu.

492
00:36:55,599 --> 00:36:57,199
Song Yan!

493
00:37:01,199 --> 00:37:02,799
Song Yan.

494
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,940
What’s the matter?

495
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:08,860
Well...

496
00:37:10,060 --> 00:37:12,360
Long time no see.

497
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:14,040
Yes, pretty long.

498
00:37:18,519 --> 00:37:22,180
Have you been well the past years?

499
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:24,780
Not too bad. And you?

500
00:37:27,719 --> 00:37:29,319
Not good.

501
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:34,703
Is there anything else?

502
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:39,480
Thanks for just now.

503
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,435
I did it for my buddy.

504
00:37:42,462 --> 00:37:43,697
And regarding last time...

505
00:37:43,697 --> 00:37:47,160
Xu Qin, what do you want to say?

506
00:37:51,199 --> 00:37:53,859
Do you have time to have a cup of coffee?

507
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,340
Do you?

508
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:06,039
Many people want to treat me to coffee.

509
00:38:06,039 --> 00:38:07,839
You need to get in line.

510
00:38:10,199 --> 00:38:12,259
I'll call you when it's your turn.

